                        <h3>What have we learned?</h3>
                        <ul>
                                <li>Always use a strong password.</li>
                                <li>Don't use the same password.</li>
                                <li>Install programs from trusted sources only.</li>
                                <li>Be careful when you open an email or a link.</li>
                              </ul>
                        
